item.title: Html HELP!
item.dc:creator: @3_Days_Grace 3 Days Grace
item.description:
@3_Days_Grace wrote:

[quote=“Natey, post:2, topic:337830”]**THIS WAS TAKEN FROM HERE.

<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Your Webclient</TITLE>
<META HTTP-EQUIV="PRAGMA" CONTENT="NO-CACHE">
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<applet name="yourclientname" width="765" height="503" archive="client.jar" code="client.class">
<param name="java_arguments" value="-Xmx1024m">
</applet>

</BODY>
</HTML>

there ya’ go.[/quote]

okay but for the archive do i just leave it like what it is? well because when i jarred my client this is what it said “Client Updated please try again” “Connection Error - Retrying in 5…4…3…2…1” and the number gets larger and larger when ever the seconds is done…
what should i do?
